{"tid":666528,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"漫畫家黑岩善宏離世享年55歲","createTime":"2018-05-16T02:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T05:07:38.000Z","uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa4377318d7d04eeebb30991e29d15c2642f0f9","tid":666528,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nT48qKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnT48qKz.jpg&h=e92831c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逝世\t2018年5月8日（55歲）<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/黑岩善宏\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%BB%91%E5%B2%A9%E5%96%84%E5%AE%8F&d=duMjyfxHMcZJy4sLcEKbzAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=29ce5f0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/黑岩善宏</a>"},{"pid":"50a5d5597412fdebd0705df30498e8275482dc30","tid":666528,"uid":39628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"以《鬼神童子ZENKI》作品走紅的日本知名漫畫家黑岩善宏，在本月8日因為心肌梗塞逝世，享年55歲，黑岩的妻子在今日才公開他的死訊。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《Sponichi》報導，黑岩的妻子今日在黑岩的部落格上，跟社會大眾報告這個「重大消息」，內文顯示黑岩善宏在本月8日因為心肌梗塞去世。黑岩的妻子也說，黑岩走得突然，家族為他辦後事，來不及在第一時間跟大家報告。他的妻子還表示，黑岩生前受到多人愛戴與照顧，雖然想一個一個親口說，但最後還是決定利用網路向大家報告這個消息，也謝謝各位支持黑岩的粉絲們。<br />\n<br />\n黑岩最早在集英社《月刊少年Jump》出道，也刊登過不少人氣漫畫，他的部落格幾乎每天都會更新，但最後更新日期停在本月7日，如今卻傳出他逝世的消息。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"15872953948ac89b776f55019772b45ca7389412","tid":666528,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:38:21.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好鐘意佢啲畫風<br />\n但唔知點解鬼神童子之後紅唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55826da7c88039188de2f807e8a8200cb62903dc","tid":666528,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"首歌仲記得點唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  hero ZENKI ZENKI"},{"pid":"ea6d676c0e8f228da23542490a20f63754e7e925","tid":666528,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"R.I.P."}]}